This product uses PostgreSQL technologies, including but not limited to:
- PostgreSQL 18.3+
- pgvector extension (VECTOR data type + HNSW/IVFFlat index)
- pg_trgm extension (trigram fuzzy search)
- pgcrypto extension (column-level encryption)
- pg_cron extension (scheduled jobs)
- Row-Level Security (RLS) policies
- PL/pgSQL server-side functions

